'''WTA阿布扎比女子网球公开赛'''（Abu Dhabi WTA Women’s Tennis Open）是一项于2021年在[[阿拉伯联合酋长国|阿拉伯联合酋长国]][[阿布扎比|阿布扎比]]举办的一年期女子职业网球赛事。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.wtatennis.com/news/1943551/wta-announces-start-of-2021-tour-season |title=WTA announces start of 2021 Tour season |access-date=2021-01-12 |archive-date=2021-05-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210502061834/https://www.wtatennis.com/news/1943551/wta-announces-start-of-2021-tour-season |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://gulfnews.com/sport/uae-sport/abu-dhabi-to-kickstart-womens-tennis-season-with-new-event-in-january-1.76007652 |title=Abu Dhabi to kickstart women’s tennis season with new event in January |access-date=2021-01-12 |archive-date=2021-02-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210205180134/https://gulfnews.com/sport/uae-sport/abu-dhabi-to-kickstart-womens-tennis-season-with-new-event-in-january-1.76007652 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。当年赛事属于WTA500赛事。在{{link-en|阿布扎比国际网球中心|Abu Dhabi International Tennis Centre}}的[[網球場|室外硬地球场]]上举行。最终白俄罗斯选手[[阿丽娜·萨巴伦卡|阿丽娜·萨巴伦卡]]获得冠军。

